A x (B x C) = {((1, 4), 6), ((1, 5), 6), ((2, 4), 6), ((2, 5), 6), ((3, 4), 6), ((3, 5), 6)}

Comparing the two sets, we can see that:

(A x B) x C = A x (B x C)

Thus, both sets are equal.
